androidx.constraintlayout.widget.Constra:
//Includes
//layout_width="match_parent": Will stretch to fill the entire width of its parent container.
//layout_height="wrap_content":  Will adjust dynamically to fit its content.
//margin: Seperates from other elements
//padding: Ensures text does not touch the edges
//textColor="@color/onBackground": Defines the text color using a color resource.
//textSize="14sp": Sets the text size to 14sp (scalable pixels).
//fontFamily="@font/inknut_antiqua_regular": Sets a custom font from the res/font/ directory. The font file inknut_antiqua_regular.ttf should be placed in res/font/.
//letterSpacing="0.02": Adds slight spacing (2% of the default spacing) between characters for better readability.
//lineHeight="25dp"(Requires API 28 or above): Ensures each line of text has a minimum height of 25dp, improving readability.
//autoSizeTextType="uniform": Enables automatic text resizing while maintaining uniform scaling to fit within the view.
//elegantTextHeight="true": Optimizes text rendering, making it visually appealing by properly adjusting the height of characters, especially in complex scripts (useful for languages like Arabic, Devanagari, etc.).
//gravity="start": Aligns the text to the start (left for LTR languages, right for RTL languages).
//justificationMode="inter_word" (Requires API 26 or above): Justifies the text by adding space between words instead of characters, creating a cleaner paragraph alignment.
//tools:targetApi="p": Specifies that this layout preview should target API level P (Android 9.0, API 28) when viewed in Android Studio.
